Interact with the Solana Network
Choose the Network:
Solana supports multiple networks (mainnet, testnet, devnet). You can configure the CLI to use a specific network:

 
 
solana config set --url https://api.devnet.solana.com
Check Your Balance:

 
 
solana balance
Transfer SOL:
To transfer SOL to another account, use:

 
 
solana transfer <RECIPIENT_ADDRESS> <AMOUNT>
